Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　劫持巴士的恐怖分子的要求是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　他们要求立即撤出驻在阿尔泰的维和部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:16.64,Note3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}艾亚利兹行政府　赫其萨贡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及释放为接受审判而关押在我国Desperate监狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那基·泰·阿尔泰前大公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波曼准将　报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Madam！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被占据的是往返于东部国境与首都之间的长途巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人质连同乘务员在内共十名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子们在车内设置了炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁说要求得不到满足的话就引爆炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下　总统选举迫在眼前的这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对应失误的话选情的前景将不容乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是警察在处理么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12分钟之前　我们国家安全保障局已接过了指挥权
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DELTA-乙HiME部队已经在现场就位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据阁下的命令　任何时候都能突入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然对方手上有人质
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就不可轻易出手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对应要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战名为“Silent Sea”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“寂静的大海”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过奖了　阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定静静地去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的　已经像平常那样派人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被她逃了~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是已经说过那种大小的石头已经没效了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-1　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-2　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-3　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Target in sight　任何时候都能射击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待机　多萝茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须避免给对方造成不必要的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平静地　冷静地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Silent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:29.24,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(475,10)}第二幕　暴·风·雨的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了　波曼准将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准将由我们这边安静地 秘密地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我释放人质　堂堂正正地决一胜负！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准将！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿米特吉准将！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准将！好好教训一下那些恐怖分子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈拉德队长　表演个节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好　冷静　冷静…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子已经迟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦　伊莉娜·伍兹?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　听得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西还真方便呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?　爱莉卡·梦宫果然是在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车型呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了　胆小鬼　快回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个大嗓门的女人是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Meister遥·阿米特吉　克利桑德的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个破坏的阿米特吉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步走错后果可是不堪设想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白　那是我的馒头…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临时中断与石上候选人的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士劫持事件似乎有新的动态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影机转向那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出来的话我这边就要动手了　你们这群恶党
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！过来的话我就把乘客全部炸死！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有艾亚利兹之魂的人才不会被炸弹什么的炸死呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从加尔德罗贝赶来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责指挥的是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?　是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为DELTA的队长可是失职了呢　千绘·哈拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些非正式的话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫神山消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连真白女王和Meister舞衣都…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧　我不是说过了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦　你认识Meister舞衣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然认识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个开拉面店的女孩子吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说想开连锁店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就叫她本店设在艾亚利兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经给了她忠告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有　在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下了要去搜寻真白陛下的字条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister爱莉卡也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的追踪呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　已经找到了她所乘坐的长途巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能解决吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点　我会帮你们一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人的来历已经查明了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被认定是主谋者的人确实是原阿尔泰的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出身于陆军近卫师团的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场状况怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被准将大闹一场以后　现在陷入了胶着状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风花市事件的情报还错综复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战略乙HiME限制交涉也近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许失败呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人　要松饼吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛还这么镇静啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就是束手无策吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破这种状况不就是我们的工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说强行突破什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请镇静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算放着不管　事态也总会有变化的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说不穿舞斗服就强行突破也太那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨拉·加拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要履行乙HiME的义务　跟舞斗服什么的没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好~好~　是气势吧　气势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占据巴士的恐怖分子的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下届总统最合适的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石上　石上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了大家的希望　期待的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亘·石上来倾听各位的要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁放那个家伙过去的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位恐怖分子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊你这疯女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亘·石上　总算见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在电视上狂批雪之和我的就是你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不会明白那是为什么的　遥·阿米特吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位国民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此粗野又暴力的人居然进入国政的中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你更让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利桑德和阿米特吉是艾亚利兹的智慧和灵魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚下去　奇怪的帽子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啰哩八嗦了　我们做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火大!　才不呢　那种事情是我做的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道为什么我能忍受如此的侮辱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道为什么吗　遥·阿米特吉?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为交了女朋友啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　正因为有爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能突破重重困难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后　我会为了爱肃清这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这份洋溢的感情　要向艾亚利兹全体国民…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前好像是个画人像的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　在全世界前介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久将成为这个国家的第一夫人的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Sweet Honey 锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是这边吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真碍事　受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是烦这种蠢男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友绘·玛格丽特?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识这个家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瓦尔基里部队的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为好玩而出卖自己人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大坏蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴　你们这群垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一夫人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大错特错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲手解决了石上的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是新的总统候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友绘君　收手吧　看上去真让人痛心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧　请给我投下纯洁的一票　接受我的支配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要自己在那大吵大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不给我认真谈判的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把这家伙的脑袋轰碎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾亚利兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇　准将　千绘前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不要察觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister爱莉卡·梦宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多么幸运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我放弃做家务而出来是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说　抢巴士的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看看这个奇特的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是…瞧　就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“星灭者”的爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那么了不起的事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还没明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉卡　给我收拾掉这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的哟~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白不在　我现在没办法使用乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次请你做我们的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人…人质是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的孩子怎么这么傻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚睡醒时谁都是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情真好　爱莉卡·梦宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的我回家看电视了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是友绘?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艾亚利兹共和国总统　雪之·克利桑德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲自来和你们交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　乘上巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我就听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换　我要求你们释放人质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多事情就拜托了呢　准将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把她也放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说她是大公殿下最大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾亚利兹决不会屈服于恐怖主义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且　连风花王国都会变成你们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶说过　打女人的男人是最差劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧　雪之小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢　爱莉卡也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我无论如何都想自己去找到真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是小遥不见的话　我想我也会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是我不是总统的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之小姐和准将从来不吵架吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我和小遥之间有个规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规矩?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　要是我做错的话小遥会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是小遥做错的话　我会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后两个人好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到两人都觉得正确的道路时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就毫不犹豫地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃五柱之一　银河的蓝玉　萨拉·加拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求备用系统给予认证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.79,Note3,NTP,0,0,0,,Surrogate System
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:53.63,Materialise,NTP,0,0,0,,Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小遥一定会做我认为是正确的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的乙HiME　遥·阿米特吉准将
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了　雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐　怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎战　快开火　开火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑架人质　威胁我们释放那基
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借助别人力量的你们　从一开始就没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要报仇的话　就用自己的双手　堂堂正正地去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是子兽?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.67,Note3,NTP,0,0,0,,CHILD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对像认定为敌对性生命体！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DELTA Force　迎战！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准将！雪之小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥·阿米特吉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持有珠洲之黄玉的吾之乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以吾之名　解放汝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下　准将
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以总统之名　把你打成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请快去避难　克利桑德阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你　Meister萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人　你看到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…不　那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真祖大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白的金刚石　Grand Meister　二三·姬野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DELTA　Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真祖怎么可能会袭击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我来揭露你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要抱到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要追得太深
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Luck！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遥！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搞背后袭击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就交给你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准将…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准将…准将！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:48.46,Note4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}艾亚利兹境内　Desperate监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾呢　被释放的机会溜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~那群人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算跟那些劫持巴士的人走　也很快就会被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况最后失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可救药的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说我聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一日三餐还能午睡　我挺喜欢这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用像在黑之谷那样被强制劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说　黑之谷里发生什么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　黑之谷消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白和舞衣也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我　那基先生　大家在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就是说“他”来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　该说是“她”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到加尔德罗贝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被干掉的乙HiME们的纳米机器发生硬化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有生命反应　身体却硬得像矿石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的只是很少的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记载在我从阿尔泰的遗迹里找到的文献里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:16.39,Note4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,450)}{\1c&HC9CAC8&}阿尔泰公国　黑曜宫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:28.75,Note4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}{\1c&HC9CAC8&}（俗称）　条纹亭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在条纹团的根据地办Meister学校真的好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你还说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城里的大官们有事的话让他们来这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算Peace Maker也和一般的小混混没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜托你的那个东西呢　小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真打算要去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从回到这里以后我就很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的东西都那么油腻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为讨厌这里才去了加尔德罗贝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被降职了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的发泄吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛~虽然我不是很赞成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听传闻说你们五柱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管闲事　小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister朱丽叶特·奈绪·张
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把客人带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了　奈绪前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:26:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS}{\fs76}{\3c&HAB45BC&}缟之舞{\3c&HD35765&}/少女的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:50.05,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(350,300)\move(280,190,480,190)}{\1c&H13EEFA&}{\3c&H1D88D9&\bord3\be1}老虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.06,0:25:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　找我有什么事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.22,0:25:50.05,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\move(400,280,300,280)}{\1c&H13EEFA&}{\3c&H1D88D9&\bord3\be1}你要成为老虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.30,0:25:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来做下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.37,0:25:52.81,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\move(510,280,510,150)\fn@Arial Unicode MS\frz-90}{\1c&H0393AF&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1}{\bord8\t(0,300,\bord3)}最强！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.66,0:25:52.81,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\move(250,150,250,230)\fn@Arial Unicode MS\frz-90}{\1c&H0393AF&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1}赌上最后的舞斗服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.10,0:25:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为这种事情把我叫来吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.60,0:25:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.67,0:25:55.25,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\fn@Arial Unicode MS\frz-90}{\1c&H864EBD&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\fs25\t(\fs80)}乙HiME们的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.40,0:25:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨拉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:25:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们根本不懂什么是下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.01,0:25:57.82,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\move(480,220,380,280)}{\1c&H13EEFA&}{\3c&H1D88D9&}炽热的战斗即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.01,0:25:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来给你们做示范
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.60,0:26:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到的话就做做看啊
